# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# Aether Backend — Environment Variables
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# Copy this file to .env and fill in real values.
# All services use free-tier plans only.
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ── Server ──────────────────────────────────────
PORT=3000
NODE_ENV=development

# ── Database (Neon PostgreSQL) ──────────────────
# Sign up: https://neon.tech → New Project → Copy connection string
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:password@ep-xxx.neon.tech/aether?sslmode=require

# ── Auth (Neon Auth) ────────────────────────────
# Optional: Neon Auth JWKS URL for production token verification
# Found in: Neon Console → Project → Auth → JWKS URL
# If not set, tokens are signed/verified using DATABASE_URL-derived key
NEON_AUTH_JWKS_URL=

# ── Grok / xAI (AI Copilot) ────────────────────
# Sign up: https://console.x.ai → API Keys
XAI_API_KEY=xai_PLACEHOLDER
GROK_MODEL=grok-3-mini

# ── Cloudinary (Image Storage — Issue Photos) ───
# Sign up: https://cloudinary.com → Dashboard → API Keys
CLOUDINARY_CLOUD_NAME=your_cloud_name
CLOUDINARY_API_KEY=your_api_key
CLOUDINARY_API_SECRET=your_api_secret

# ── Razorpay (Finance Payments — Test Mode) ─────
# Sign up: https://razorpay.com → Test Mode → Settings → API Keys
RAZORPAY_KEY_ID=rzp_test_PLACEHOLDER
RAZORPAY_KEY_SECRET=PLACEHOLDER

# ── Resend (Email Notifications) ────────────────
# Sign up: https://resend.com → API Keys (3000/month free)
RESEND_API_KEY=re_PLACEHOLDER

# ── Firebase FCM (Push Notifications) ───────────
# Sign up: https://console.firebase.google.com → Project Settings → Service Accounts
FIREBASE_PROJECT_ID=your-firebase-project-id
FIREBASE_PRIVATE_KEY="-----BEGIN PRIVATE KEY-----\nPLACEHOLDER\n-----END PRIVATE KEY-----\n"
FIREBASE_CLIENT_EMAIL=firebase-adminsdk@your-project.iam.gserviceaccount.com

# ── Sarvam AI (Indian Language Translation + Voice) ──
# Sign up: https://dashboard.sarvam.ai → API Keys
# Primary provider for Hindi, Tamil, Marathi, Telugu translation
SARVAM_API_KEY=

# ── LibreTranslate (Fallback Translation) ───────
# Falls back to this if Sarvam is not set
# Public instance (free): https://libretranslate.de
LIBRE_TRANSLATE_URL=https://libretranslate.de

# ── DSpace (PYQ Paper Scraper) ──────────────────
# Your university's DSpace REST API endpoint
DSPACE_BASE_URL=https://your-university.dspace.edu/rest
DSPACE_COMMUNITY_ID=PLACEHOLDER

# ── CORS ────────────────────────────────────────
# Comma-separated list of allowed origins
ALLOWED_ORIGINS=http://localhost:8081,http://localhost:5173,http://localhost:3001,exp://localhost:8081
